{"tid":583058,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【九巴秋後算賬】反大聯盟車長貼標語力撐九巴：公司今次決定做得好","createTime":"2018-03-06T16:46:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-07T00:48:14.000Z","uid":20058,"like":1,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"233686ccff6e4e75324f8ed4b4eb1e8a8b706be4","tid":583058,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T16:46:33.000Z","msg":"九巴疑秋後算賬，今日突然解僱早前發起罷駛行動的「月薪車長大聯盟」發起人女車長葉蔚琳及其丈夫劉卓恆，以及另外2名車長。到晚上7時35分，葉蔚琳和丈夫在昂船洲車廠見記者講述事件，不少網民和車長均力撐四人，惟有「反大聯盟」車長隨即在九巴車廂的駕駛座貼出標語，「公司今次決定做得好」力撐九巴做法。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》晚上收到由車長轉發來的兩張相片，聲稱是「反大聯盟」車長在車廂貼出的標語，內容為：「支持公司決定，我們車長們會繼續安全駕駛，為巿民服務！」、「我們是有紀律的，駕駛為巿民服務，我們車長會繼續安全，公司今次決定做得好！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180306/57913175\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180306%2F57913175&d=UW%2F8ApER6lIp2DYUhoFWCzM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=cf8368b8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180306%2F57913175&h=b2b611ae\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180306/57913175</a>"},{"pid":"e031fb41154ff3cefd76e3b558fa5f48d9976f64","tid":583058,"uid":20058,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T16:48:34.000Z","msg":"呢樣真<br />\n我有個舊同學就係九巴司機<br />\n佢地話呢樣嘢爭取左好多年終於有<br />\n根本好多人唔知行情又突然正義向左走向右走上身<br />\n想攪大件事唔俾佢沉可以間接受惠<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=CA&amp;message=6870003\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Ftype%3DCA%26message%3D6870003&d=UW%2F8ApER6lIp2DYUhoFWCzM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=584a110c\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=CA&amp;message=6870003</a><br />\n<br />\n高登<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e08c3bd7bb89f75b91d928f2d3